2580               * ATOI convert string to integer (used in VAL and tokenization)
2581               * R5 contains pointer to string (caller responsible for advancing TXTPTR if applicable)
2582               * R0=10, R1=character, R2=char copy, R3='9', R4='0', R6=negative, R8=value, R9=clobbered by multiply
2583               * R7 must be preserved for LET destination address
