2619               * ITOA convert integer to temporary string (used in PRINT)
2620               * R5 contains value
2621               * R0=character 0, R1=10, R2/R3=don't care/place value, R4/R5=division result, R6=leading 0 flag, R7=pointer to temporary string area (LINBUF)
